{"type": "article", "id": 14340, "title": "‘collo-alto’餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-03T07:12:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000307U28TdD7ASfc6jewv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 Inga Sempé 新推出的餐具组 ‘collo-alto’，将代表意大利厨卫品牌艾烈希（ Alessi ）参加今年9月份的巴黎家居装饰博览会。‘ collo-alto ’翻译过来是“高颈”，体现出这套餐具细长的风格。另外，它的型号非常齐全，并拥有细致的分工，喝汤、吃点心、吃鱼都有对应的刀叉，体现出越来越精致的生活理念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141928nQDUg6xYkJNreK1s.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"844\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.03178484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261419288ODrhlUWR1MzgINK.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141929qVkXln710c9poRPK.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261419290vRkSfTPI3wOgioZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"618\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}